		<item>
		<title>Premio Maccio Capatonda 2011: i vincitori</title>
		<link>http://prejudice.kekkoz.com/2011/08/05/premio-maccio-capatonda-2011-i-vincitori/</link>
		<comments>http://prejudice.kekkoz.com/2011/08/05/premio-maccio-capatonda-2011-i-vincitori/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 05 Aug 2011 07:30:53 +0000</pubDate>
